=== replicate.glp ===
Non-ground term replicator.
Goal: replicate2(Xs, Ys1, Ys2) or replicate3(Xs, Ys1, Ys2, Ys3)

Replicates incrementally-constructed terms with uninstantiated readers.
Suspends on readers, resumes when values available.

Variants: replicate2 (binary), replicate3 (ternary), generalizes to n copies.
Cases: ground guard, suspension/resumption, incremental replication
